NSSM instructions for EdgeOS watchdog (Windows)
1) Download nssm from https://nssm.cc/download
2) Install service (run elevated):
   nssm install EdgeOSWatchdogDaemon "C:\Path\To\python.exe" "C:\Path\To\repo\services\watchdog_daemon.py"
   Set Startup directory to the repo root.
3) Environment:
   WATCHDOG_DRY_RUN=0
4) Start service:
   nssm start EdgeOSWatchdogDaemon
5) Logs:
   reports/watchdog_daemon.log
